<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>TrumpsPocketbook</title>
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag    'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
    <%= javascript_include_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Bitter|Adamina" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-2.2.3.min.js"></script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="cover">
      <div class="pop-up">
        <p>This app is a satire web app, and <strong>the results of the generator should not be taken seriously.</strong>
          The opinions that get generated by the Trump Opinion Generator are snippets taken from Trump's interviews, debates and speeches.
          One of these opinions will be randomly generated from a database of positive and negative messages.</p>
          <p>This app was a personal project and unorthodox exercise to practice database models, associations and data migrations.</p>

          <button class="agree">I UNDERSTAND</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    <div class="bar">
      <h1>TRUMP OPINION GENERATOR</h1>
      <h2>MAKE AMERICA GREAT AGAIN!</h2>
    </div>
    <% if flash[:message] %>
      <div class="flash"><%= flash[:message] %></div>
    <% end %>
    <div class="shell">
      <%= yield %>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Disclaimer: This web app is entirely satire, and the results should not be taken seriously.</p>
      <p>This is a David Rhie web app.</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
